You'll need 1.21.0 of Fog for `clone_volume`
- update bundler.d/fog.rb

Set up a compute profile for the temporary machine (say, 1Gb ram, 1Cpu, 1 net
device, 5G disk)

You'll want to send a request like this:

```
POST http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/v2/hostgroups/:id/snapshot

{
  "host": {
    "compute_resource_id": 3,
      "compute_profile_id": 1,
      "compute_attributes": {
        "image_id": "",
        "image_ref": ""
      }
  }
}
```

Unsetting the image id/ref is important.

Enjoy
